snippet.title: Sonic Superstars - Shadow Costume
snippet.description:
To celebrate the announcement of Sonic X Shadow Generations, a new Shadow the Hedgehog costume is available in Sonic Superstars! Download it for free today!

Purchase Sonic Superstars today at: https://www.sonicsuperstars.com
